metadata.name: Magic
metadata.description:
Mint 2 tokens to get the redeem one in next 7 days.  
If you want to see the redeem token, let's see it on my twitter page. Join me!

Cry for love,  
Cry for disappointment,  
Weep for it, and it will be good,  
and upgrade yourself to strength like a withered Lost Roses,  
and someday it will blossom again.
